PrecisOrder fixing the dates on which different provisions of this Act [BILL C-6], being chapter 5 of the Statutes of Canada, 2000, shall COME INTO FORCE, as follows: . (a) MONDAY, MAY 1, 2000 - Parts 2 [Electronic Documents], 3 [Amendments to the Canada Evidence Act] and 4 [Amendments to the Statutory Instruments Act], and (b) MONDAY, JANUARY 1, 2001 - Part 1 [Protection of Personal Information in the Private Sector]. .
